         <abstract id="aspace_c93228f62ddedc957af35b8d73deb860">The records consist of financial records, minutes, and officers' books for the Yale Forest Club and School of Forestry alumni. Also included is a Yale School of Forestry register, 1900-1907. Also included are records and a videotape documenting the 2003 alumni weekend.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
